<tr><td>Microsoft 365 Apps</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td><strong>Non supportato su LTSC</strong>; richiede OS con Modern Lifecycle</td></tr>
<tr><td>.NET 8 (LTS)</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td>EOL: Novembre 2026</td></tr>
<tr><td>.NET 9 (STS)</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td>EOL: Maggio 2026</td></tr>
<tr><td>Power BI Desktop</td><td class="warn">&#9989;*</td><td class="warn">&#9989;*</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td>Funzionante; supporto LTSC non dichiarato esplicitamente</td></tr>
<tr><td>Visual Studio 2022/2026</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td><strong>Policy esplicita:</strong> "VS isn't intended to run on LTSC". IoT Enterprise blanket-escluso</td></tr>
<tr><td>SSMS 22.x</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td><strong>Esplicito nella doc:</strong> "Windows Enterprise LTSC editions" non supportate. IoT escluso</td></tr>
<tr><td>SQL Server 2022</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td>Mainstream support fino a Gen 2028</td></tr>
<tr><td>Microsoft Teams (new)</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ko">&#10060;</td><td class="ok">&#9989;</td><td><strong>Bloccato dal 15/08/2025 su LTSC.</strong> Funziona su IoT GA</td></tr>
